settings.question: Why is KYX different?
settings.Answer: Buying sneakers online can be tough! We try to make it as easy and stress free as we can. By authenticating all of our sneakers before we list them, to professionally cleaning them so they feel like new to you, and using our photography and KYX Rating so you can feel more comfortable with your purchase.

settings.question: How soon will I receive my order?
settings.Answer: We ship Mon-Fri. And we’ve already authenticated and processed all of our listings. So we can ship your kicks to you, faster. Standard Shipping arrives in 3-7 business days and Express in 2-4 business days.

settings.question: What payment methods are accepted?
settings.Answer: We gladly accept Visa, MasterCard, American Express, Discover, Apple Pay, Google Pay, PayPal, Meta Pay, Venmo, and Shop. We also offer Shop Pay Installments.

settings.question: What if I have more questions?
settings.Answer: Visit our main FAQ page. Also, feel free to use our chat feature in the bottom right corner. And you can also use our Contact Form.
